{"tid":1635332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂牆新方向 革命輸出","createTime":"2019-10-07T13:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:15:07.000Z","uid":86524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"291d2e69c79453c86da22c98cb13a030267a9f28","tid":1635332,"uid":86524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:03:47.000Z","msg":"而家呢場活動去到瓶頸位 唔上唔落咁<br />\n好似國慶過埋都咩起息<br />\n<br />\n小弟喺到諗，周街都仲係好多大陸人，<br />\n尤其是大學裡面好多大陸學生。<br />\n不如痴多啲大陸醜聞，中共極權嘅文宣落連儂牆，<br />\n一黎多啲藍絲睇到大陸黑暗嗰面，<br />\n二黎大陸學生、旅客都會知多啲真相。<br />\n<br />\n思想先係最難改變嘅，我諗中共怕呢啲多過淨係喺香港嘅示威。始終我地點搞，對大陸人，對佢地嘅權勢都冇直接影響，不如直接督佢地死穴<br />\n<br />\n譬如好多大陸人，藍絲都冇聽過新疆集中營<br />\n其餘例子仲有<br />\n打壓宗教自由，毀觀音像<br />\n北京紅黃藍幼稚園虐待/集體性侵事件<br />\n抗生素濫用最嚴重國家<br />\n瘦肉精事件<br />\n假雞蛋<br />\n地溝油<br />\n毒奶粉<br />\n假疫苗<br />\n離奇死亡原因，如生粉刺死、躲貓貓撞牆死、李旺陽被自殺等<br />\n京A8特權車牌刪文事件<br />\n<br />\n我一人之力搵唔到咁多新聞，又唔識整靚靚文宣<br />\n希望大家可以一齊幫手革命輸出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後 光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea63ceffdc6e85d1d87f1f7e278b0c6ad780966","tid":1635332,"uid":86524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2608dccd881d602fb7a81dd8dade7ff5ca6880","tid":1635332,"uid":86524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e559c76eab3487d3a7b7ae08133fda5e6614add","tid":1635332,"uid":86524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d770f479cd39c5fdf7bce21843dedb92c344165","tid":1635332,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"講返樽頸好唔好? 定係你係one of 中國人?"},{"pid":"8ba389543d4861cae73623b0f682c61ed6699462","tid":1635332,"uid":86524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d770f479cd39c5fdf7bce21843dedb92c344165","tid":1635332,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"講返樽頸好唔好? 定係你係one of 中國人?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"係咪到呢個時候都仲要乜都屌？<br />\n好心著雷劈"},{"pid":"25cca912fb026d1d8f9b64c54696e275e553397d","tid":1635332,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"之鋒一出聲，馬上踢爆分化五毛所謂休息唔裝修既風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5d43e03b67c608c9b28188345bf08c3c2d67a0ec","tid":1635332,"uid":8414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"我老母雖然淺黃晚晚睇直播晚晚屌警察，但我同佢講紅藍黃幼稚園既事佢都係唔信（已經share晒新聞俾佢睇），有咩計可以拆？"},{"pid":"86bdb1ebed41ea8782d7ffbb9ef0c0f5a59ae161","tid":1635332,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba389543d4861cae73623b0f682c61ed6699462","tid":1635332,"uid":86524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d770f479cd39c5fdf7bce21843dedb92c344165","tid":1635332,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"講返樽頸好唔好? 定係你係one of 中國人?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"係咪到呢個時候都仲要乜都屌？<br />\n好心著雷劈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:15:07.000Z","msg":"係, 因為你消滅緊香港本土文化"}]}